---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section class="py-12 sm:py-8 md:py-12 lg:py-14 xl:py-12 2xl:py-28 h-screen">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] xl:max-w-7xl">
    <div class="lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <div
          class="max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-0 xl:max-w-5xl 2xl:max-w-6xl"
        >
          <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center gap-4">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-between">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mx-auto">
                <h1
                id="bannerH1"
                class="font-helvetica text-center text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl sm:tracking-tight lg:text-[3rem] xl:text-[4.5rem] xl:tracking-tight 2xl:text-[5rem]"
              >
                Reliable & Affordable
                
                <!-- <span class="text-[hsl(280,100%,60%)]">Next.js</span> app -->
              </h1>
              <h1 id="bannerH2" class="font-black leading-none flex">
                <span class="text-[hsl(200,100%,60%)] text-[8rem]"> Bulk</span>
                <div class="p-4"></div>
                <span class="whitespace-nowrap text-[hsl(240,100%,70%)] text-[8rem]">
                SMS</span
              >
            </h1>
             
              </div>
              
              <div class="text-white text-center flex items-center justify-center flex-col">
                <p class="text-sm w-2/3">
                  Conversations via Short Message Service (SMS) are an important
                  element of the consumer experience. If your company isn't taking
                  advantage of this service, you're passing up a cost-effective
                  approach to interact with your customers.
                </p>
              </div>
             
              <div class="flex w-full flex-col items-center">
                <div class="relative mt-4 flex h-full xl:mt-8">
                  <button
                    class="relative flex cursor-pointer flex-row items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-t3-purple-200/20 bg-t3-purple-100/10 px-2 py-2 text-sm transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-t3-purple-300/50 hover:bg-t3-purple-100/20 md:px-3 md:py-3 md:text-lg lg:px-5 lg:py-4 lg:text-xl"
                    title="Copy the command to get started"
                    id="command"
                  >
                    <a href="https://app.philsms.com/auth/login" id="command-text" class="text-white">Get Started</a>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    #bannerH1 {
      font-family: 'DistantGalaxy', sans-serif;
    }
    #bannerH2 {
      font-family: 'DistantGalaxy', sans-serif;
    }

    #check-icon {
      stroke-dasharray: 450;
      stroke-dashoffset: -30;
      animation: draw 2s linear normal;
    }

    @keyframes draw {
      to {
        stroke-dashoffset: 200;
      }
    }
  </style>
</section>
